8. If one data type value is assigned to ‘a’ variable and then a different data type value is assigned to ‘a’ again. Will it change the value. If Yes then Why?

Solution :

a = 1
a = "j"
print(a)

Yes the value will change since the variable a has been assigned a new value. Python will change the variable type if the variable value is set to another value.

